p: H1299 cells were seeded in 24‐well plates at a density of 1 × 10 5 cells/well. After overnight incubation, cells were treated with SFE at 500 μg/ml for 24 hr. The media were collected and analyzed for matrix metalloproteinases‐2, ‐7, ‐9, and ‐10 levels using enzyme‐linked immunosorbent assay kits (Koma Biotech Inc.) following the manufacturer's instruction.
